song_name: Still Got A Long Way To Go

version_description: Hey all, I've decided to give this track a crack. I'm hoping that this will be the next big campfire song, with folks trying to imitate Jimmy Barnes' scorching vocals. A couple of notes: The G Am F progression is easiest done as barre chords. During the synth build up (C G Am G), you can play the Am with a quick stab of the 1st fret of the e string (or the 6th fret of the B string if you're playing with barre chords). https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rvrZJ5C_Nwg.
